{"tid":713068,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"每人都有二十歲初的迷惘？(求職)","createTime":"2018-06-22T14:13:18.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-23T10:49:03.000Z","uid":78377,"like":10,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"04dc3343dcac6ecb68a61868cce7ba5a40308219","tid":713068,"uid":78377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T14:13:18.000Z","msg":"近來成日見到人自殺 都係2X歲初<br />\n本身係諗 有無咁啱<br />\n但其實自己都係正值呢個時段 而且成日覺得好迷惘<br />\n<br />\n未來當然值得迷惘 因為響香港生存 真係好難<br />\n但我睇近少少 即係畢業 <br />\n呢排全世界一係仲interview緊 一係等緊offer <br />\n準備interview 就會不停諗自己同同輩既比較 究竟自己揀呢條路/呢個職業係啱唔啱 <br />\n過程會不斷質疑自己既能力 個性 <br />\n等offer都可以好痛苦 每一刻你都等緊D野 等緊自己想要既野<br />\n但去到最後 你幾努力準備 都可能付諸流水<br />\n一路等 你就會不停諗 期間其實你又會準備下一個interview<br />\n<br />\n準備interview同等offer未必係好長既過程<br />\n但係呢兩三個月你會覺得特別長 好似輪迴咁<br />\n更甚係你會見到身邊既同輩讀得書 揾到份好工 / 屌你老母去撚左幾個旅行點解仲有錢架<br />\n就會不斷質疑自己 想揾一樣野推動自己努力<br />\n<br />\n希望揾緊工既人 唔好放棄 加油<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"394a5518babc2f420a97d01584ca02aeb847fed2","tid":713068,"uid":78166,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T14:17:41.000Z","msg":"等緊intern offer<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67ad1e7aa6571253633e8118ed89454401aea0bb","tid":713068,"uid":78377,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"394a5518babc2f420a97d01584ca02aeb847fed2","tid":713068,"uid":78166,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T14:17:41.000Z","msg":"等緊intern offer<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T1